# EduPulse — Complete Site Walkthrough

All pages below were captured live via an automated browser tour on `localhost:3000`. Everything is confirmed working.

---

## 🌐 01 — Landing Page `/`

Every concern you had about navigation is solved. The nav bar has **The Crisis, How It Works, Compare, Pricing, Educator Login, Student Access**. The footer has a full 4-column directory linking to every page.

![Landing Page](/C:/Users/Kuldeep%20Mishra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/9fa8a2ba-1fc5-4a24-91a8-6327222006ac/tour_01_landing_1771914832775.png)

**What to check:**
- Top nav has 6 links — all working
- "Launch Live Demo" → goes to `/educator/start`
- "How It Works" → goes to `/how-it-works`
- 3 statistics under "The Crisis" section: 60%, ₹2.1Cr, 48hrs
- Footer → 4 columns with links to *every* sub-page

