## 🛡️ 03 — Admin Panel `/admin`

Central command center — now has a full navigation grid linking to all sub-pages.

![Admin Panel](/C:/Users/Kuldeep%20Mishra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/9fa8a2ba-1fc5-4a24-91a8-6327222006ac/tour_03_admin_panel_1771914870275.png)

**What to check:**
- "All Platform Sections" grid — 7 coloured tiles linking to Start a Class, Learning Outcomes, Traction, Testimonials, LOI Generator, ROI Calculator, Competitive Analysis
- Signal Button Management: Real DB — you can add/delete signal types live (currently: "I'm Confused", "Too Fast", "Need Example")
- High confusion is highlighted in **red** (22%, 27%) vs normal in grey (17%)
- Danger Zone: Reset button works with password auth

