## 📲 04 — Educator QR Launchpad `/educator/start`

Where every class session begins. Teacher projects this on the classroom screen.

![Educator Start](/C:/Users/Kuldeep%20Mishra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/9fa8a2ba-1fc5-4a24-91a8-6327222006ac/tour_04_educator_start_1771914912586.png)

**What to check:**
- 4-digit PIN is auto-generated (random every time)
- QR Code points to `edupulse.com/join/[PIN]`
- "Initialize Dashboard" button navigates to the live dashboard for that PIN

---

## 🎛️ 05 — Educator Dashboard `/educator/dashboard?session=XXXX`

The teacher's cockpit during a live lecture. Logged in as `ram@edupulse.com`.

![Educator Dashboard](/C:/Users/Kuldeep%20Mishra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/9fa8a2ba-1fc5-4a24-91a8-6327222006ac/tour_06_educator_dashboard_1771914957298.png)

**What to check:**
- **Topic Annotation bar** at the very top — type `"Slide 5: Recursion"` and press Enter to log it with a timestamp
- **Topic Timeline Annotations** panel in the bottom-right — shows all logged topics with timestamps and marks the current one "CURRENT"
- **Time-Series Confusion Matrix** — Recharts area graph, updates every 3 seconds, shows the last 30 minutes
- **Current Confusion Load** — live percentage
- **Real-time Assistant** — AI text that changes based on signal patterns
- Session PIN visible in the header (e.g. 5555)

---

## 📱 06 — Student Join Page `/join/[PIN]`

What a student sees after scanning the QR code. No account needed.

![Student Join](/C:/Users/Kuldeep%20Mishra/.gemini/antigravity/brain/9fa8a2ba-1fc5-4a24-91a8-6327222006ac/tour_07_student_join_1771914972756.png)

**What to check:**
- Anonymous — no login required
- Session PIN visible on screen (confirms they joined the right class)
- Two buttons: "I'm Confused" and "Too Fast"
- After clicking: 60-second countdown timer appears
- Signals go directly to the teacher's dashboard for that PIN only

