## ✅ Summary — What's Real vs Simulated

| Feature | Status |
|---|---|
| QR Code + PIN Generation | ✅ **Real — generates unique codes each time** |
| Student signal submission | ✅ **Real — writes to Supabase** |
| Session isolation (signals per room) | ✅ **Real — filters by PIN/session_id** |
| Recharts Timeline Graph | ✅ **Real — polls Supabase every 3 seconds** |
| Topic Annotation bar | ✅ **Real — client-side timestamp log** |
| Educator login (Supabase Auth) | ✅ **Real** |
| Signal types (Add/Delete) | ✅ **Real — writes to Supabase** |
| Data Reset | ✅ **Real — password-protected** |
| Admin metrics (Active Classes, 1420 signals) | ⚠️ **Simulated numbers — for demo** |
| ROI Calculator sliders | ✅ **Real — formula-based** |
| Competitive Comparison | ✅ **Static content — accurate** |
| Learning Outcomes | ✅ **Seeded demo data** |
| Traction Dashboard | ✅ **Simulated live-updating counter** |
| Testimonials | ✅ **Seeded demo data** |
| LOI Generator | ✅ **Real input → formatted document output** |
